{"type": "article", "id": 9508, "title": "Dual Land 系列灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-13T07:37:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235413zr2JXwPumAbO835D.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自荷兰阿姆斯特丹的设计工作室 Faberhama 由 Paola Amabile 和 Alberto Fabbian 两位设计师创办，他们始终坚持在传统中进行现代化的创新。这个叫做 “Dual Land” 的系列灯具灵感来自远古的荷兰须德海和威尼斯的海洋文化，在过去，金属框架玻璃灯担任着海上照明的重任。他们把传统的玻璃吹制与 3D 打印相结合，试图唤起人们对遗忘的物体的回忆。<a href=\"http://www.faberhama.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是工作室的主页</a>，感兴趣的话可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235409lJCY7Z5aokEjWLfO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235409UhrPDzoncFQs95uZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235409D0X1zPq5i6kgldbf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.08958333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235410cOwMWnG6D2Nv3H8U.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235411mRldMj3SkF2h1V9A.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235411n90BiDgTRfMFX5dA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235412JqFAf9I6Cl5Doa2r.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}